<div class="page-content">

  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> March 2026</p>
  <p>This privacy policy explains what information Deal Drops (<a href="{{ site.url }}">{{ site.url }}</a>) collects, how we use it, and your choices. We keep things straightforward — no legalese.</p>

  <h2>What Data We Collect</h2>
  <p>We keep data collection to a minimum. Here's what we may collect:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Analytics data</strong> — pages you visit, time spent, device type, and general location (country/city level). This is collected through Google Analytics and is anonymised.</li>
    <li><strong>Cookies</strong> — small files stored in your browser by us and our partners (details below).</li>
    <li><strong>Voluntary info</strong> — if you contact us via email or social media, we'll have whatever you share with us.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect passwords, payment details, or any personally identifiable information through this website.</p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>Our site uses cookies for the following purposes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Essential cookies</strong> — to remember your preferences (like dark mode).</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — Google Analytics uses cookies to understand how visitors use our site. You can opt out using the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>Advertising cookies</strong> — Google AdSense may show personalised ads and uses cookies to do so. You can manage your ad preferences at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>Affiliate cookies</strong> — when you click an affiliate link (e.g., Amazon), the retailer may set a cookie to track the referral. This is how we earn a commission at no extra cost to you.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Affiliate Links Disclosure</h2>
  <div class="disclosure">
    <strong>Important:</strong> Deal Drops is a participant in the <strong>Amazon Associates Program</strong> and other affiliate programmes. When you click a deal link and make a purchase, we may earn a small commission at <strong>no extra cost to you</strong>. This commission helps keep the site free. All affiliate links are marked with <code>rel="nofollow sponsored"</code>.
  </div>

  <h2>Google AdSense</h2>
  <p>We use Google AdSense to display advertisements on our site. Google AdSense may use cookies and web beacons to serve ads based on your previous visits to this and other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your browsing history.</p>
  <p>You can opt out of personalised advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>. Alternatively, you can visit <a href="https://www.aboutads.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener">aboutads.info</a> to opt out of third-party cookies for personalised advertising.</p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — website traffic analysis</li>
    <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — advertising</li>
    <li><strong>Amazon Associates</strong> — affiliate product links</li>
    <li><strong>Netlify</strong> — website hosting</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Each of these services has its own privacy policy. We encourage you to review them if you have concerns.</p>

  <h2>Your Choices</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.</li>
    <li>You can opt out of Google Analytics tracking.</li>
    <li>You can use an ad blocker — we won't hold it against you.</li>
    <li>You can contact us to ask about any data we may have related to you.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>Our site is a general-audience deals website. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected such information, please contact us and we will remove it promptly.</p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. When we do, we'll update the "last updated" date at the top. For significant changes, we'll make it obvious on the site.</p>

